  "detailed_description": "Modiverse provides an open multiplayer sandbox environment, where you can build complex physics based worlds using tools and props. It allows complete game-modes such as TTT, Deathrun, RolePlay and more. There are countless fun game modes and maps to experience. You can even build your own tools, props, levels or complete game-modes using our extensive mod kit!",
